Mapping out an app or any project.

Always jot down how you plan to set out your app or any project ... no matter how simple:

1.  create 4 pages, add, subtract, multiply and divide
2.  Create 2 random number
3.  Create a form to answer flashcard
4.  Create a submit button
5.  Create a new card button
6.  Code to determine the correct answer
7.  Code to determine if our answer equals the correct answer
8.  Output answer to screen.
